            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Helvius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Pol</abbr><ex>lia</ex></expan> Fus<lb break="no" n="3"/>cus |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>LV <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Ianuarius <lb n="7"/>et Modestus <lb n="8"/>liberti <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zeile 2: kleines S am Zeilenende; Zeile 7: T mit Überlänge; Z. 8: I-longa. Im Giebelfeld von Schlangen umrahmtes Gorgoneion, daneben Rosetten. Unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes Ansatz eines weiteren gerahmten Feldes.</p>
            </div>
